  "text": "Despite being among the most drought tolerant cereals, the sorghum plant can suffer significant damage during its development, under strong water stress [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] . Sorghum damage caused by drought stress is greater during reproductive stages than during the vegetative stage.",
